<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4F46E5;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4F46E5;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Waitlist!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello<%= @lead.company_name.present? ? " from #{@lead.company_name}" : "" %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for joining our wholesale marketplace waitlist as a <strong><%= @user_type %></strong>. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
        
        <% if @lead.user_type == 'brand' %>
          <p>As a brand, you'll soon be able to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Grow your wholesale business with better commission rates</li>
            <li>Get paid faster with capital advances</li>
            <li>Connect with retailers that are perfect for your products</li>
            <li>Access detailed analytics about your performance</li>
          </ul>
        <% elsif @lead.user_type == 'retailer' %>
          <p>As a retailer, you'll soon be able to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Buy on your terms with flexible payment options</li>
            <li>Order without minimums across multiple brands</li>
            <li>Discover products that match your store's unique profile</li>
            <li>Access seasonal planning tools for better inventory management</li>
          </ul>
        <% end %>
        
        <p>We're working hard to build a platform that reimagines wholesale and creates better connections between brands and retailers. We'll keep you updated on our progress and let you know when we're ready to launch.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The Wholesale Marketplace Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> Your Wholesale Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to <%= @lead.email %> because you signed up for our waitlist.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>